review_data.title: Great brunch buffet
review_data.content: Llegamos a este lugar para probar el brunch buffet. Armamos una tabla de quesos veganos exquisitos, muy rica textura y sabor. Además comimos hummus, fruta y unos postres deliciosos. El lugar es choro, la gente y la dueña muy buena onda, pero no es barato...More

review_data.title: Friendly service, great food
review_data.content: We came for brunch with friends on a Saturday. A very nice restaurant with authentic interior and warm colors - the place to be in Zurich Wipkingen. All service personnel was very friendly, helpful and attentive. Food and drinks from the buffet tasted really great...More
